1. 如何配置sysmon client?
sysmon-client是作为erl-crontab的task运行, 所以我们应该拷贝
我们需要的*.beam文件到erl-crontab的ebin目录下, 使这些beam可以被erl-crontab加载.

a. 如何配置sysmon client?
   client模块所有的配置信息在sysmon_client_api_config.hrl中.
   可以做相应的修改.

b. 手动拷贝client_api和crontab_task下面所有的模块对应的beam文件到目标路径.
   我们提供了一个脚本自动安装:
   sudo ./install_client.sh /usr/local/erl-crontab

c. 修改erl-crontab的配置文件crontab.cfg, 增加任务:
例如:每5分钟做一次定时任务
{{"0-59/5", "*", "*", "*", "*"}, {monitor_app_task, run, ['ejabberd', 'cpu']}}.
{{"0-59/5", "*", "*", "*", "*"}, {monitor_app_task, run, ['ejabberd', 'memory']}}.
{{"0-59/5", "*", "*", "*", "*"}, {monitor_app_task, run, ['dispatchserver', 'cpu']}}.
{{"0-59/5", "*", "*", "*", "*"}, {monitor_app_task, run, ['dispatchserver', 'memory']}}.
{{"0-59/5", "*", "*", "*", "*"}, {monitor_app_task, run, ['redis', 'cpu']}}.
{{"0-59/5", "*", "*", "*", "*"}, {monitor_app_task, run, ['redis', 'memory']}}.
{{"0-59/5", "*", "*", "*", "*"}, {monitor_app_task, run, ['mysql', 'cpu']}}.
{{"0-59/5", "*", "*", "*", "*"}, {monitor_app_task, run, ['mysql', 'memory']}}.

d. 启动erl-crontab
sudo ./bin/crontabctl start


2. 如何配置sysmon server?
a. sudo ./install_server.sh /usr/local/sysmon
b. 修改配置文件etc/sysmon.cfg
c. 启动sysmon server
   sudo ./scripts/sysmonctl start

